# Build context filter for the OpenHammer multi-stage image (spec 16).
# Excludes regenerated/heavy artifacts, secrets, and loop/agent state so `COPY . .`
# stays lean and never leaks host `node_modules`/`dist` into a stage (which would
# override the in-image `npm ci`/`npm run build` and break platform resolution).

# Dependencies & build output (regenerated in-image via npm ci / npm run build)
node_modules
dist
coverage

# VCS
.git
.gitignore
.gitattributes

# Local environment & secrets (keep the example for reference)
.env
.env.*
!.env.example

# Build-loop & agent tooling state
.loop-complete
.claude

# Logs
*.log
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*

# Docs & planning (not needed in any image stage)
README.md
LICENSE
docs
specs
PROMPT_*.md
AGENTS.md
IMPLEMENTATION_PLAN.md
loop.sh

# Docker metadata (not needed inside the image)
Dockerfile
.dockerignore
